{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act34side", "eventName": "生路", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "BP-2", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "評議式迎接", "storyInfo": "在深海獵人計劃曾經的技術顧問布蘭都斯的幫助下，歌蕾蒂婭等人證明了自己的清白與安全，但烏爾比安的嫌疑卻難以洗脫。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "51_g6_aegirarena", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loading_intro", "key": "$loading_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1400_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌蕾蒂婭執政官，您認為問題並不在於那場戰役本身？", "name": "軍團長官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1400_1#1$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。詳細的作戰部署此刻正投影在各位面前，如果其中存在我沒能注意到的紕漏，你們每個人都有義務指出。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1400_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我對具體的作戰部署沒有疑問。結合當時的認知條件，那無疑是最合理的作戰部署。", "name": "軍團長官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1400_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我希望知道，現在的您會如何評判當時的認知條件？", "name": "軍團長官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1400_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "必須承認，阿戈爾當時對海嗣的認知存在嚴重的缺陷……", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "char_263_skadi#4"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "char_263_skadi#4", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些人想說什麼？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前還在阿戈爾的時候，你就不喜歡想太多，你還是不習慣那些人的思考方式。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們對我們沒有惡意，他們只是在尋求必要的事實。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尋找所有可能的缺陷，質疑所有完美的成果。然後，真實與美，還有正確的道路，將在最激烈的爭論中彰顯自身。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一切交給劍魚吧。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是不想聽，就閉著眼睛睡一下子。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……綜上，五年前那次戰爭設計最大的失誤，就是沒能為我們的認知缺陷留出餘地。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在泰拉的真相被揭開之前，我們需要承認自己對海嗣的認知總會存在缺陷，我們的戰爭設計必須將其考慮在內。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1400_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同意。您剛剛得出的結論，應該被用於審視未來可能誕生的各項作戰計劃。", "name": "軍團長官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1400_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能與您一同反思一場已經被塵封的戰役，並得出有效的結論，是我的榮幸，歌蕾蒂婭執政官。", "name": "軍團長官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1400_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1397_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，除了五年前的那場戰役……", "name": "科學院研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有更加現實的問題值得我們擔心。", "name": "科學院研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "根據體檢報告，您、斯卡蒂、勞倫緹娜，三位都發生了不容忽視的身體異變。", "name": "科學院研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我無意質疑各位對國家的忠誠，但我需要知道海嗣基因對各位的同化，會對各位接下來的行動產生怎樣的影響。", "name": "科學院研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請原諒我這麼發問。", "name": "科學院研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彌利亞留姆很快就要完成對所有巢穴的定位，在那之後，海嗣將在第Ⅳ級武器的作用下被驅離，航道正式開啟。", "name": "科學院研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這個時間點上，深海獵人，是否會成為阿戈爾的敵人、你們自己的敵人？", "name": "科學院研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.5, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對阿戈爾來說，失控的獵人比海嗣本身更加危險。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深海獵人，就像是阿戈爾的反面。他們誕生於阿戈爾最卑劣的傷口，阿戈爾憐憫他們，也畏懼他們。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "深海獵人，烏爾比安，對吧？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line66"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "按理說，你更應該在底下接受質詢。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line68"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你比我想像中要冷靜很多，也知道我的身分。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來歌蕾蒂婭在陸地上建立的信任關係，並不只是對那位醫生一人。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有在之前的任何一次行動中見過你。你不是伊比利亞的審判官，也不是島民。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位羅德島的醫生將你帶到阿戈爾，卻又有意隱藏你的身分。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我只是凱爾希的同僚。;我和她同屬於羅德島。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line79", "option2": "line79"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨你怎麼定義自己。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，你能幫到獵人們。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "有事為什麼不直接找斯卡蒂？;有事為什麼不直接找幽靈鯊？;有事為什麼不直接找歌蕾蒂婭？", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line86", "option2": "line89", "option3": "line94"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line97"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡蒂不太擅長這樣的事情。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line97"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是說勞倫緹娜？", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不太擅長這樣的事情。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "3"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line97"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在並不是合適的時機。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 98, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "你不信任獵人們？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line101"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恰恰相反，我信任她們，而且太過了解她們。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#2$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡蒂的行動快過思考，勞倫緹娜清醒的時日尚淺，最終決定一切的人只會是歌蕾蒂婭。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "此前我已經向她分享過許多情報，她應該有了警惕。她並非不清楚自己會遭遇多少限制，但仍然選擇回到阿戈爾。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她太急於回到熟悉的環境，殊不知自己已經被擺在了最顯眼的位置，一切可信任的和不可信任的都有十足的權力來審視她。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在並不是深海獵人返鄉的最好時機，這是一場豪賭。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "既然如此，你為什麼還要潛入這座城市？;看來你還是很關心獵人們。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line113", "option2": "line113"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌蕾蒂婭她們的處境不容樂觀。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與我不同，她們三人雖然接受了改造，卻沒有參與深海獵人計劃最核心的研發工作。她們很難解釋清楚自己身體的異變。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會告訴你一些相關的訊息，必要的時候，我需要你想辦法為歌蕾蒂婭解圍。事後，再向她傳達我的提醒。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於更多的事情——", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許，各位可以聽我說兩句。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……布蘭都斯。他也來到了這裡？", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "布蘭都斯？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1381_1#8$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每次都是這樣，以前在研究所的時候，你也好，烏爾比安也好，總是趁我打盹的時候和研究員們吵起來。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#8$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "顧問，你的意見確實會很有參考價值。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1381_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不勝榮幸。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#8$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾是深海獵人計劃的技術顧問，負責改造實驗中的基因嵌合研究。換句話說……", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1381_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "此時此刻，我是這座城市最了解深海獵人的人。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#5$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌蕾蒂婭、勞倫緹娜、斯卡蒂，她們在乾燥的環境待了太久，其間依然頻繁地進行戰鬥，她們的身體情況確實不容樂觀。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#5$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "布蘭都斯", "content": "各位的擔心很有道理。但我的答案是，"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1381_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "布蘭都斯", "content": "不會——"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她們並不會變成海嗣。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#8$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寂靜。"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "布蘭都斯清了清嗓子。"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1381_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我盡量說得簡單些。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#8$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們都知道，海嗣基因在尋常生物體內會展現出異常的性狀控制力，不可逆地抹消該生物的本來屬性。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們在深海獵人身上盡可能地延長著這種海嗣化的過程，直到它遠遠長於獵人的自然壽命。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但後來，技術院的研究取得了關鍵性進展。在獵人們出發去斬殺“初生”前，我們為他們每人都安排了一次“自適應接點”手術。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“自適應接點”被安置在人類基因與海嗣基因的嵌合處，它能幫助深海獵人對海嗣基因保持更密切的“監視”。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一旦海嗣基因表現出異常的性狀控制力，“自適應接點”就會催使獵人的身體進行抵抗，防止海嗣基因奪取控制權。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儘管獵人們的“自適應接點”已經在未經維護的情況下運行了五年，難免會有老化，但她們如今的異變都尚在預期範圍之內。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1397_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "顧問，根據深海獵人研究所當年的記錄，“自適應接點”手術曾經出現過一場手術事故。", "name": "科學院研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1381_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那場事故發生在……烏爾比安身上。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#2$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但記錄應該也有說明，經過多次臨床驗證，我們已證明那場事故沒有產生任何不良影響。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以對此負責，也願意為此接受質詢。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然深海獵人回到了阿戈爾，那麼她們的身體狀況就是可控的。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1397_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽起來，您已經有了控制獵人身體異變的可行手段？", "name": "科學院研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城內就有一間閒置已久的深海獵人研究所，可以被重新啟用。之後，我可以親自為她們進行“自適應接點”的維護。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1397_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，烏爾比安呢？", "name": "科學院研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1397_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位至今不願回歸阿戈爾的深海獵人，我們該如何確保他不會墮落成海嗣？", "name": "科學院研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是說，我們擔心的事情已經發生了？", "name": "科學院研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "話題的焦點突然轉移到了你身上。;聽起來你很危險。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line195", "option2": "line195"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們的懷疑很合理。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對超出掌控的事物保持十二分的警惕，是常識，也是來之不易的教訓。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "懷疑你的不只場上的那些人。;我也好奇你隱藏行跡的原因。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line203", "option2": "line203"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "你潛入城市，真的只是出於對獵人的關心？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line205"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯圖提斐拉沉沒之前，我曾向歌蕾蒂婭分享我的發現——海嗣中存在著不只一隻類似伊莎瑪拉的超級個體——“初生”。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而此時此刻，新的“初生”已經“鬆動”，祂，或祂們，甦醒在即。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不確定數量，不確定時間……但是很近。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line213"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海嗣向陸地的遷徙與之相關。這段時間，我深入了足夠多的巢穴，海嗣的反應共同傳遞出某種……危機感。", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許連如今的海洋都不足以供養這場覺醒？新“神”的甦醒，是另一場陸地人口中的大靜謐，還是其他形式的海洋災難？", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這場浩大的遷徙與阿戈爾的航道計劃幾乎同步發生，那麼，彌利亞留姆在其中到底處於怎樣的位置？", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些是否足夠讓我來到這座城市？", "name": "烏爾比安"}, "figure_art": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海嗣固然能在本能的驅動下獨立繁衍，但它們源於“初生”，不可能違背最基本的生物性。", "name": "技術院科研人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "換言之，即使那隻“初生”的死亡沒有遏止海嗣的進化，也不至於使它們爆發式地湧現出前所未見的特質。", "name": "技術院科研人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您似乎忽視了我在任務書裡提到的最新情報。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“複數的初生”，這樣的解釋很合理，可我對烏爾比安的質疑恰恰來源於此。", "name": "技術院科研人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "計劃周詳的行動以失敗告終，倖存的三位獵人隨著海浪來到陌生的陸地，與那位在巢穴中滯留到最後的獵人重逢。", "name": "技術院科研人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“海中存在複數的初生”，烏爾比安帶來的這一情報不僅具有顛覆性，而且非常“有效”。", "name": "技術院科研人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它恰如其分地解釋了為什麼明明你們完成了作戰目標，卻催生了海嗣更大的異動。它回應了所有人的疑問。", "name": "技術院科研人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您對這一情報的疑問在於？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣恰到好處的解釋，要麼是唯一的真相，要麼是針對所有疑問設計出的答案。", "name": "技術院科研人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是否採信烏爾比安傳遞給您的情報，會對我們接下來的戰爭設計產生重大的影響。", "name": "技術院科研人員"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然烏爾比安還活著，那麼確認他的行跡與狀態，甚至與他當面對證，就是最直接有效的驗證方式。", "name": "技術院科研人員"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "布蘭都斯顧問，你已經沉默了許久。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "關於烏爾比安的情況，你有什麼想要補充的嗎？", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你與烏爾比安師出同門，甚至你加入深海獵人計劃，也是出於對烏爾比安的信任——你一開始並不贊成這項計劃。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我同樣信任你作為阿戈爾人的專業與德行，你不必刻意迴避什麼。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1381_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執政官閣下，我只能說，我必須對今天在這場評議會中說過的每一句話負責。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#5$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "烏爾比安……我不會故意進行任何有利於他的假設，也不想給出任何不利於他的猜想。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#5$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1381_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "僅此而已——", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#2$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "看來你和那位顧問的關係不錯。;原來再冷酷的人也有這樣的朋友。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line265", "option2": "line265"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "烏爾比安沒有回應你。場上的質詢仍在繼續，但布蘭都斯不再說話，他突然抬起頭看向你所在的方向，像是感應到了什麼。"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隔著大半個鬥智場，你對上了他那雙有些疲憊的眼睛。"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他明顯注意到了什麼，坐在他身側的執政官，以及相鄰的幾個阿戈爾人都捕捉到了那一瞬間的異樣，部分人的目光追了過來。"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……;呃……", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line271", "option2": "line271"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你側過身，不知何時，身旁的座位已經空了。"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我？我只是個旁觀的陸上人而已。;不好意思，我打擾到你們了嗎？;我也需要發表意見嗎？", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line275", "option2": "line275", "option3": "line275"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "透過這場評議會，我們已經得出了充足的結論。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌蕾蒂婭、斯卡蒂、勞倫緹娜，以及其他深海獵人，為阿戈爾付出了巨大的犧牲，也做出了偉大的貢獻。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時隔五年，我們仍有機會從她們的見聞與經驗中汲取出新的想法，這是阿戈爾的榮幸。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，她們證明了自己的清白與安全，證明了她們在航道計劃進行至此的緊要關頭回歸，不是威脅，而是助力。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而，與此同時，無數疑點聚焦在另一位倖存的深海獵人，烏爾比安身上。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出於不可知的原因隱匿蹤跡，並試圖影響其餘的深海獵人——這些行為顯著違背了他身為深海獵人的責任。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "根據現有的消息，我們無法確定他究竟懷著何種動機，意欲達成何種目的，甚至連他現在是否還能被稱為阿戈爾人都未可知。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "烏爾比安必須盡快被找到。即使他真如同歌蕾蒂婭所說的一樣不懷惡意，也必須接受質詢，以洗清自己身上的重重嫌疑。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "疑惑已經得到解答的各位，你們可以離場了。尚有疑問的人，質詢可以繼續。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌蕾蒂婭執政官，你還有什麼想要補充的嗎？", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#3$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "51_i05", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.4, "yScale": 1.4}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"yTo": 0.0, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 100.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鬥智場中央的珊瑚狀終端緩緩合攏、收縮、下沉，最終沒入地面以下。水紋盪漾的場地平坦而空曠，彷彿是要容納一場戲劇演出。"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "場地中央，唯有歌蕾蒂婭一人。"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經告訴了你們我所知的一切。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我對評議會的結果沒有意見，對烏爾比安的嫌疑，也不持任何異議。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已經陸續有人離場，他們在出口轉身，默契地向歌蕾蒂婭頷首致意。"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "餘下的聽眾仍在發問。歌蕾蒂婭應對著她知道或不知道答案的問題。"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "穹頂投下的水紋與縈繞場地的光紋相交織，卻沒能在歌蕾蒂婭的臉上映照出任何表情。"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "51_i05", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.0, "yScale": 1.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"yTo": 0.0, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 100.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕我是個阿戈爾人，有時候也搞不懂這種狀況。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明明上一秒還在唇槍舌劍針鋒相對，下一秒又在感謝歌蕾蒂婭對阿戈爾的付出。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們是真誠的。科學要求人們把情感與事實分開，而他們確實做到了。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當然知道這些人是真誠的，我只是……唉，算了。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三隊長目前也只是受到懷疑，劍魚、博士和凱爾希都會想辦法的。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來我們去哪裡？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等劍魚來找我們吧。這場評議會一時半會還沒辦法完全結束。唉。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼也突然嘆氣？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劍魚以前常去當時那座城市的鬥智場看戲劇演出，除非有戰鬥安排，否則每場都去。我有時候會跟著她一起去。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二隊長她……", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劍魚的藝術造詣蠻高的，據說是被她母親培養出來的。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是和一般的觀眾不一樣，她喜歡坐在最高最遠的位子上，搞得我每次都得和她分開坐。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在她看來，保持適當的距離，就可以盡可能地排除干擾。忽略一些場地上的細節，反而能更好地體會故事本身。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而此刻，她自己卻成了站在劇場中央的人。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她習慣的距離感被完全消解，她成了被審視、剖析、討論的對象。在那個位置，沒有人可以保持從容。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鯊魚，我突然也明白自己剛剛因為什麼嘆氣了。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為什麼？", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到此刻，我才確認我們真的回到了阿戈爾。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}